Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:06.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the idiot hero, we now have to join the Princess Recovery Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:09.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,General Godwin and Lady d'Arquien began their fight in the fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:13.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Yuki and Rico are involved in this crazy ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've got my hands full with Genoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:19.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, you'd better save my princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:12.90,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)\pos(429,359)}  「Fierce Battle! Myon Castle!」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess is coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:30.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul's Imperial Guard Army, Genoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:13.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, these three are just idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:17.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, once they're in battle, they're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:36.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad. You're good enough for me to treat you as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:43.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's time to show you the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:46.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The purpose of our wars is for others to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:51.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Power, magnificence, and straightforwardness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are the qualities of a knight and warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make these powers prevail,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we have Ki Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:05.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ki Power unleash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lion King's Claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:55.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did my Lion King's Thunder Blast combo feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the legendary Ki Power supreme attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't end it yet, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Normally it would've ended already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still able to stand? You're a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy was able to put up that sort of defense within a split second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it did work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah! Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're not from here,\N I guess you can't turn into a pet ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not try anything beyond your...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No thank you. Your worry is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:52.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I somehow got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ki Power is this kind of feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't hurry, we won't make it in time for the concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for the princess's song!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? C-Concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, wait, Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What concert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's reinforcements have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:51.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:02.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo is here on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the city gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:20.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, Princess Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Lady d'Arquien.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't call me princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm now a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Excellency...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside, d'Arquien.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business with Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My sincere apologies. This is a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:47.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, as a rear unit guardian of the youngsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that I have to force my way through?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not think I am still who I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:02.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Not even you can stand in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I shall face you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the war at the fortress is still going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:27.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I wonder if the princess can still make it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to hear the princess sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:36.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the knights and the hero are trying their very best right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Your Excellency,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard you're continuously attacking our country?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a routine war activity for us, the Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Your Excellency's attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:05.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the diligent Leader of the Knights in my country is stressed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:11.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention my princess's concert and usual activities are unable to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's your doggie princess's problem!{sigh.. this anime is so peaceful...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She organized a sweet potato digging competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And some random water sport competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are those going help exercise the youngster's bodies?! {literally, cool down the youngster's blood cells.. i duno what that means but it is probably for them to release stress or y'know.. to move around...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:27.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they do seem kind of happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything about being unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:39.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is that not everything can be settled so simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:43.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our princess does have her weak points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:46.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as she matures and gathers more experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:49.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll be able to be an even \Nmore outstanding leader in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I truly believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, for now, please just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:10:00.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice if... that was possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:10.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what others say! I will do it my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was superb. I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Godwin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:49.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was really amazing, Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You only needed one strike to finish off that knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:56.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She barely used twenty percent of her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She let us through on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To be fair, I used no more than thirty percent myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, make that around twenty percent as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! So, is there really gonna be a concert after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I already say so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:23.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Those Genoise idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They got me into trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you mumbling about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the quack hero of Biscotti!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Quack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You meddling kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you playing on the battlefield?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:54.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:05.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency, my apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:07.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it'd turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother. It's the fault of the two idiots over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency? Um, it's been so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:23.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Princess Millhiore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:27.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for disturbing the \Nwinning country's celebratory party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:33.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize on behalf of my ill-mannered brother for bringing you here by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:37.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. Prince Gaul didn't know that{\fscx230}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll consider other ways to compensate for this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge, do take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we still make it on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have twenty minutes before \Nthe princess is to appear on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take an hour just to get to the hall from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?! What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:13.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should we do? What should we do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:12.10,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, we'll definitely get spanked if we wake up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.39,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pretend to be unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:16.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pretend to be unconscious... Unconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:18.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to send you back, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You send her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:42.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...use my Hero's Special Delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember it already! It's Gaul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:07.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered how you used your Ki Power, Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get going, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:23.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already familiar with Ki Power and Crest power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've memorized most of it. I'll memorize all of it soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady d'Arquien!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brioche, I haven't seen you for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, and the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:53.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending the princess back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Sir Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the Knights of Biscotti, leader of the Omitsu Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze Panettone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:19.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you! I've seen how dynamic you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:24.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite confident in my legs, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, we can take turns carrying the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:31.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the offer, but that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just thought of a way to increase my speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll release Ki Power by using the crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by following the level I imagine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:42.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then transforming it into the actual pattern and power. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:43.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can probably do this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That was cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Miss Yukikaze...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop the "Miss"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Yukikaze, I'll go ahead first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:09.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boost Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sir Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:47.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you overuse Ki Power, there'll be terrible consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. This is much easier than running.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I've wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:11.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I became the leader of Biscotti just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:17.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the members of the Knight Army were from my father's generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a leader, I'm a complete novice. I can't seem to do anything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:26.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've made so much trouble for Sir Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:33.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! There was no trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:36.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been a day since I was summoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:39.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,yet I've already had so many extraordinary experiences!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was able to meet a cute princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:49.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, isn't it good to be a novice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also a novice in terms of being a hero. A novice hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a novice can fly if he tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:04.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you give your best every day, you'll become someone great someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what my teacher taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:08.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be an impact, so hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:29.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being late. Millhiore has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minutes 'til show time.{"un" from "until" is removed, so apostrophe goes before "til"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:36.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Makeup artist, costume artist, please take your places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lecture you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the flow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Amelita. It won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:19:00.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's welcome Princess Millhiore Frianno Biscotti on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:13.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During the war today, the hero who came to Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:16.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the knights who have been fighting for our country the entire time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,have brought us victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For today's victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:26.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and to provide a better tomorrow for everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing my heart out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"This Must Be Love"
