Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved she made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the hero okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He used his Ki Power so recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:12.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, yeah. He's totally burned out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you just come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to have a second celebratory party!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:20.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
